Material3 (recommended)Core only <p>If your app uses Material3, depend on <code>waypoint-material3</code>. It includes <code>waypoint-core</code> transitively.</p> <pre><code>// build.gradle.kts
kotlin {
    sourceSets {
        commonMain.dependencies {
            implementation(libs.waypoint.material3)
        }
    }
}
</code></pre> <p>If you do not use Material3, or you want full control over tooltip UI, depend on <code>waypoint-core</code> alone.</p> <pre><code>// build.gradle.kts
kotlin {
    sourceSets {
        commonMain.dependencies {
            implementation(libs.waypoint.core)
        }
    }
}
</code></pre>
